title: ZombieLeninism
author: MrBollings
pages:
#-         What Is§0
§0    ZombieLeninism?§0
§0-------------------§0
§0
§0An introduction to the§0
§0lessons taught by Dear Leader himself.§0
§0
§0
§0
§0
§0Published by the Workers' Party.
#-   The start of this story takes us back before CivCraft 1.0, to a server called Golden Creeper. Here, ZombieLenin started the first Leningrad. In this new city, the Workers' Party - lead by Dear Leader himself - was the guiding force of society, and right
#- -fully so! The Workers' Party was made up of those who ZombieLenin could trust, and formed the strong, central pillar of Leningrad society.§0
§0  Citizens of the city were given direction and hope by the Workers' Party, who lived modestly and were paid
#- only in thanks and the resources given to any other Citizen.§0
§0  ZombieLenin himself was the head of the entire operation, and was responsible for much of the internal situation, and was the outwards face of the city to others.§0
§0  This methodology of Dear
#- Leader was adopted into CivCraft as well, and formed the ideological pillars of the cities founded by the Workers' Party during 1.0. As 1.0 ended, ZombieLenin once again lead the Workers forwards, and as 2.0 started, founded New Leningrad - the shining
#- jewel of the +- quadrant! During Dear Leader's time in New Leningrad, he became very sick, as his undead form is not meant to constantly endure the stresses of life. He passed leadership of the Workers' Party to Comrade Romec, who sadly also became sick, 
#- but this time with Obsidian Lung, which he got from his tireless work for the people!§0
§0  Comrade BolleDeBoll, currently known as MrBollings, was then ushered in as the new Chairman of the Party. The Workers' Party under Comrade Bolle has flourished and 
#- survived even the end of 2.0! The Party now finds itself in CivClassic, and has set up in the city-state of Mount Augusta, where we intend to gather our strength and once again embark on the journey which Dear Leader started all those years ago!
#- 